the tollfree numbers for information about the 
distribution of the agent orange settlement fund for vietnam 
veterans have been changed officials said 
the new number is 18002254712 officials said friday 
the previous phone numbers one for new york state and one for 
the rest of the country were disconnected in order to consolidate 
them into one number at the aetna life insurance co which will be 
the claims administrator for the program 
the 240 million settlement fund resulted from a suit against 
manufacturers of the herbicide agent orange 
