held in the kent county jail pending a detention hearing 
robert bobby debarge 32 was held without bail friday in 
los angeles both men were indicted on charges they conspired with 
five others to transport cocaine from los angeles to michigan 
the brothers also are charged with two counts of using 
interstate travel to distribute cocaine and one count of 
distribution of cocaine if convicted of the conspiracy charges 
they face up to life in prison 
chico and robert debarge are members of the large grand rapids 
family known for its singing talents two years ago chico debarge 
recorded a solo album chico debarge which reached no 33 on 
the billboard charts 
