platforms owner los angelesbased occidental petroleum corp 
occidental hired adair to make the rig safe seal gas leaks and 
save the oil wells to which the rig is connected the 73yearold 
adair based in houston texas has gained fame over several 
decades by capping outofcontrol oil wells 
it seems to me there are three or four wells that are burning 
